  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive relentless waves of enemies in a neon-lit cyber dystopia!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm yourself with your weapon of choice and dive into a battle for survival against endless waves of enemies. Every kill earns you XP, unlocking powerful perks and upgrades in the shop. Level up, enhance your gear, and gain new abilities as you progress through an infinite onslaught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.poster.avif?t=1734581207\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.webm?t=1734581207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.mp4?t=1734581207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Temporary power-ups like infinite ammo, health boosts, increased damage, and speed enhancements are yours to grab in the heat of battle. Use these bonuses to gain the edge you need to outlast your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each wave intensifies, with tougher enemies and longer challenges. Stun, burn, and fight back as you hold your ground in a world where only the strongest survive.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive relentless waves of enemies in a neon-lit cyber dystopia!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm yourself with your weapon of choice and dive into a battle for survival against endless waves of enemies. Every kill earns you XP, unlocking powerful perks and upgrades in the shop. Level up, enhance your gear, and gain new abilities as you progress through an infinite onslaught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.poster.avif?t=1734581207\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.webm?t=1734581207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319710/extras/23b54e045b4b58b9371e0522e9e83a70.mp4?t=1734581207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Temporary power-ups like infinite ammo, health boosts, increased damage, and speed enhancements are yours to grab in the heat of battle. Use these bonuses to gain the edge you need to outlast your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each wave intensifies, with tougher enemies and longer challenges. Stun, burn, and fight back as you hold your ground in a world where only the strongest survive.</p>",
